    public class Association.HiddenSome<T extends ModelClass>
extends AssociationEnd<T>
implements Navigability.NonNavigable, Multiplicity.OneToUnlimited
    An immutable collection which contains the elements of a non-navigable association end with a multiplicity of 1..*.

    Represents: non-navigable association end with a multiplicity of 1..*
